dt$bias = dt$NOS
dt_reformatted = dt[,c("author_name","daytime_dysfunction_control","daytime_dysfunction_control_sd","Mean.Age.in.Controls..years.","Sex.Female.n.....control","bias")]
colnames(dt_reformatted) <- c("author_name","dd","sd","age","female_ratio","bias")
dt_reformatted$concussed = FALSE
dt_reformatted_tmp = dt[,c("author_name","daytime_dysfunction_concussed","daytime_dysfunction_concussed_sd","Mean.Age.in.Concusssed..years.","Sex..Female.n.....concussed","bias")]
colnames(dt_reformatted_tmp) <- c("author_name","dd","sd","age","female_ratio","bias")
dt_reformatted_tmp$concussed = TRUE

dt_reformatted = rbind(dt_reformatted, dt_reformatted_tmp)
dt_reformatted$variance = dt_reformatted$sd^2
dt_reformatted = na.omit(dt_reformatted)
rma.da.adjusted <- rma(yi=dd, vi=variance, data = dt_reformatted, method = "DL",
                       mods = ~ age + female_ratio + bias)
